WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:14.569
Family, I'm excited to be with you all today. First off, I just want to say thank you for all of the likes, for clicking the notification bell, and for subscribing. It is helping to get the gospel out.

00:00:14.570 --> 00:00:36.492
There are so many emails that I get telling me, 'Hey, I got born again today watching your video,'or 'Hey, I got baptized in the Holy Ghost today watching your video.'I've heard from people who were set free from addictions—people who were addicted to cigarettes and all kinds of perversions who email me and say they got set free.

00:00:36.493 --> 00:00:40.679
So I just want to let you know, thank you for all of your support.

00:00:40.680 --> 00:01:07.946
You know, there are a lot of people saying, 'Well, you're the only one seeing anything; you're the only one having these visions, and nothing's come to pass.'I just started this YouTube channel back in March, and the Lord told me there’s going to be an acceleration of all things: acceleration of the economy, acceleration in politics, and acceleration in spiritual things, like the signs in the heavens.

00:01:07.947 --> 00:01:21.565
We are going to see some amazing things in the days ahead. No man knows the day or the hour when Jesus Christ is coming, but I can tell you I have an urgency in my spirit that He's coming.

00:01:21.566 --> 00:01:30.241
I have an urgency in my spirit to tell you it's time to repent, to get on our knees, and to seek the Lord with all our hearts.

00:01:30.242 --> 00:01:43.305
We are in the last of the last seconds before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, and I want to encourage you today: don't give up on your dreams, don't give up on what God's called you to do.

00:01:43.306 --> 00:01:52.066
We've got to push. We're right at that one-yard line, right before first and goal, and we're about to make a touchdown.

00:01:52.067 --> 00:02:04.127
As the body of Christ, we've got to stand and be even stronger now than we've ever been before because great days are ahead for the body of Christ.

00:02:04.128 --> 00:02:10.275
I want to give you that encouragement before I tell you about the storms. There are a lot of people talking about the storms.

00:02:10.276 --> 00:02:17.287
I've seen people on Sid Roth, and there are other prophetic people who have seen stuff, but I was looking at people like Sister Billye.

00:02:17.288 --> 00:02:23.768
I told you all that I was caught up in the Spirit while I was praying one night, and I went before the throne.

00:02:23.769 --> 00:02:37.347
There was prayer circling in the throne—I'll put the video in the description below if you're new to my channel—but there was a pastor that I saw whom I wasn't really familiar with.

00:02:37.348 --> 00:02:43.673
I looked him up afterward and have kept an eye on him to see what's going on in his ministry.

00:02:43.674 --> 00:02:54.131
Whenever I was in the Spirit, the Lord showed me this pastor, Tracy Harris, and he has a church in Texarkana.

00:02:54.132 --> 00:02:58.902
The Lord told me to follow his ministry regarding the end times.

00:02:58.903 --> 00:03:14.091
Then you go back to what Pastor Steve Cioccolanti said; he talked about the pale, green-colored horse—the warhorse—and then the plague would come after.

00:03:14.093 --> 00:03:32.196
Well, like I said, we prophesy in part and hear in part. I see these things coming and I don't really know the dates, but I feel an urgency in my spirit. The Lord will show you things way in advance.

00:03:32.197 --> 00:03:52.049
This prophecy from Sister Billye that you're going to hear is about a storm and the economy—something happening—and then the next one we'll hear is about a plague coming greater than COVID.

00:03:52.050 --> 00:04:00.453
Pastor John Kilpatrick had a visitation from the Lord in the midnight hour warning him about a storm coming.

00:04:00.454 --> 00:04:12.919
Many men of God are hearing about a storm coming, and the Lord's warning them like little fire alarm bells going off: 'Caution, caution, caution.

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:35.150
Red alert.'There's a storm coming, but there'll be a calm after. There are going to be judgments. You can sense things.

00:04:35.151 --> 00:04:57.366
We're not talking about the Great Tribulation—you will not even be here—but here in the Ozarks, Shelly and I remember the ice storm years ago that knocked out electricity for two weeks.

00:04:57.367 --> 00:05:07.514
Trees broke everywhere. I remember it happened here in Oklahoma thirteen years ago.

00:05:07.515 --> 00:05:13.425
I had sold my house and was living in a double-wide with Shelly at Prayer Mountain until I could find another house.

00:05:13.426 --> 00:05:40.700
Terry and Lynn lived up over the firehouse. We had no heat, but we had a fireplace and lots of wood, so we made a fire.

00:05:40.701 --> 00:05:54.566
We had iron cookware and made oatmeal, boiled water, and made chili.

00:05:54.567 --> 00:06:04.866
Terry would come down on the snowmobile and help us out; he's a survivor.

00:06:04.867 --> 00:06:30.886
For a while, they had a generator. It was two weeks of below-zero weather every night.

00:06:30.887 --> 00:06:41.666
If you lived around here and moved to town, town didn't have much better, though they had some fuel.

00:06:41.667 --> 00:06:52.959
Anyway, praise the Lord. I say pretend you're in the Ozarks and there could be an ice storm.

00:06:52.960 --> 00:07:10.612
It probably wouldn't last too long, maybe a few days, so it wouldn't hurt to keep your car filled with gas, have a couple of extra cans, and have plenty of water and food.

00:07:10.613 --> 00:07:26.543
I'm not a scare tactic person; I don't want you in fear. But it doesn't hurt to have some peanut butter, tuna fish, salmon, and things in cans that you don't have to fix for two or three days.

00:07:26.544 --> 00:07:38.417
I just think it wouldn't be a bad idea. Besides, if nothing ever happens, you can eat it and drink the water!

00:07:38.418 --> 00:07:58.834
Glory be to God. You're not going to throw any stones or tomatoes when things happen according to God's calendar.

00:07:58.835 --> 00:08:04.793
She's telling everybody, not in fear, to have a Psalm 91 level of extra in your house.

00:08:04.794 --> 00:08:13.650
You can have an urgency like I'm talking about. When I was in the Spirit, the Lord showed me a massive storm coming on the East Coast.

00:08:13.651 --> 00:08:28.038
It was dark, dark purple all inside, and every once in a while, the Lord shows it getting closer and closer.

00:08:28.039 --> 00:08:41.359
The last time I saw it, it was on our shores. He showed me a massive, thick, humongous wall of protection.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:58.639
He said this wall was separating the storm from protection.

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:06.861
There were dark clouds on one side and great light on the other.

00:09:06.862 --> 00:09:12.899
He said this is just like when it was dark in Egypt and it was light in Goshen.

00:09:12.900 --> 00:09:31.910
He was telling me, 'This is Psalm.'There was a table prepared with dishes, bread, and all kinds of beautiful stuff for us as believers.

00:09:31.911 --> 00:09:50.958
There was a stream of quiet brook right next to the table, green lush grass all around it, and a little cottage with smoke coming out of the chimney from baking fresh bread.

00:09:50.959 --> 00:10:12.039
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I have prepared a table before you in the presence of all your enemies.'He said in the days ahead, you will have to have a revelation of the name, the power, and the authority of the name of Jesus.

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:21.326
You're going to have to know that you need to get Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 deep down in your heart.

00:10:21.327 --> 00:10:28.821
Put it so deep down inside of you that you don't question it. It's like it's a rhema word to you; that is what I'm talking about.

00:10:28.822 --> 00:10:35.974
You can read the word, but you have to know the word. You have to have a revelation knowledge of the word.

00:10:35.975 --> 00:10:42.045
You can just go through Genesis and read it and read it and read it, but the devil knows when you know.

00:10:42.046 --> 00:10:52.735
I'm telling you, I've seen it; I know in the spirit realm when that sword comes out of your mouth and it cuts the devil.

00:10:52.736 --> 00:11:01.672
It's either alive inside of you or it's not. You can quote it and quote it and quote it—and faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:11:01.673 --> 00:11:09.708
That's how you get rhema word inside of you: by hearing and hearing and hearing and hearing it again.

00:11:09.709 --> 00:11:15.091
Not just hearing it once, but whenever you eat it like a cow eating its cud.

00:11:15.092 --> 00:11:20.312
It sits there, and it spits up out of its stomach and it chews on that grass again.

00:11:20.313 --> 00:11:31.246
You've got to keep that word inside of your mouth, and it's what brings life. That's whenever your mountain needs to hear your voice.

00:11:31.247 --> 00:11:48.763
You have to speak to your circumstances, and that's what I'm talking about: having the authority of the believer and having a revelation of the name of Jesus, understanding who we are in Christ, seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers and might.

00:11:48.764 --> 00:11:53.781
It's not going to come just by hearing it once; it's not just going to come by hearing it twice.

00:11:53.782 --> 00:12:06.830
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing, and hearing by the word of God, getting that revelation inside of you of where we are in these end times. The Lord told me, 'Sobering days are coming.

00:12:06.831 --> 00:12:47.436
Very sobering days, very hard days for some people.'But He said, 'What's the opposite of sober?'And I said, 'Drunk.'He said, 'Be being filled with the Holy Ghost, a fresh touch from the Holy Ghost every single day, dying to self daily, getting in that river with Him and sitting at His feet on a daily basis and reading that word.'Just like I'm talking about, being that cow eating that grass over and over again until it becomes rhema word inside of your spirit.

00:12:47.437 --> 00:13:01.894
I'm telling you, it's like a light switch coming on, and that's whenever you speak that word out of your mouth and the devil—James: Submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee from you.

00:13:01.895 --> 00:13:06.313
I'm going to go to 'The Midnight Hour,'this next prophetic word.

00:13:06.314 --> 00:13:18.861
This is the man that I saw in the throne room with the Lord praying for the nations, asking the Lord for a fresh visitation from Him concerning souls and outpouring.

00:13:18.862 --> 00:13:26.561
I heard his prayers, and that's what he was praying for in 'The Midnight Hour.'This is a warning.

00:13:26.562 --> 00:13:38.592
What's amazing about this: the Lord had this visitation the same night I had the visitation going to the throne. Then he comes back and he tells what he saw.

00:13:38.593 --> 00:13:47.141
Suddenly, as I'm lying there praying in the throne room, I'm just overwhelmed with what He's saying to me about what we have and the authority of faith in that name—what we're going to do.

00:13:47.142 --> 00:14:18.883
It wasn't but a matter of minutes and He said this: 'There are things coming on the earth that, without revelation of the power and the authority in the name of Jesus, My people will not survive.'I'm trying to tell y'all—can you see why I had to build your faith before I started talking to you?

00:14:18.884 --> 00:14:25.557
You can't get caught up in the things I'm going to say, because if you're natural-minded, you're going to worry.

00:14:25.558 --> 00:14:31.088
'What is it? What's the Lord saying? What's coming on the earth?'That's not the point.

00:14:31.089 --> 00:14:41.636
The point is to stay on point, and if you'll do what I'm telling you to do, you'll survive no matter what's coming in the earth.

00:14:41.637 --> 00:14:54.565
So stay on point. I don't want to say this, but I'm bound to; in the office He gave me, I really don't want to say this because it's His church.

00:14:54.566 --> 00:15:03.151
But I have nothing else I can say about His church but what the Head of the church is telling me.

00:15:03.152 --> 00:15:07.813
I'm believing God this won't be, but I saw it and it comes up in me again.

00:15:07.814 --> 00:15:29.942
He said, 'While you're under this anointing, say it.'You're about to see in the shift: churches right now that are absolutely going and blowing, and you think, 'Oh, wow, they're doing great.'In a short time, if they will not take hold of the Full Gospel and operate in the authority of this name, they're literally going to look like somebody drove a truck through there.

00:15:29.943 --> 00:15:38.030
I mean, it's going to be cleaned out like somebody sucked them out of there—the victims: some to the curse, some dead, some in the hospital.

00:15:38.031 --> 00:15:47.599
Others will say, 'I'm not getting what I need here,'and they're going to race to the glory.

00:15:47.600 --> 00:16:00.577
They're going to rise out of darkness and come to the light. They do not have anything in their arsenal to deal with what I saw coming.

00:16:00.578 --> 00:16:16.545
The prodigal are coming home, and the weak, anemic, selfish Christians that want the church to pat them on the back are about to get an awakening, startled and sprinkled by the power of God.

00:16:16.546 --> 00:16:30.278
You mark my words: the remnant church is going to become the place to be, and they are coming from the north, the south, the east, and the west.

00:16:30.279 --> 00:16:37.020
They're going to jump in the river, and the river is going to carry you right to the perfect... Purity is going to be at a premium.

00:16:37.021 --> 00:16:44.504
It's going to be hard to find, but it won't be hard to recognize when you find it—the real from the fake.

00:16:44.505 --> 00:16:55.518
It'll be kind of rare, so it'll be hard to find, but it won't be hard to recognize it when you do find it. Glory be to God! I don't want this to happen.

00:16:55.519 --> 00:17:04.581
I don't want whole churches to be decimated, but they're going to be steamrolled by this thing if they don't rise up and understand who they are in Christ.

00:17:04.582 --> 00:17:33.851
Because churches are the bullseye of the target. God is raising up a nation within a nation and raising up some voices, young and old, that are going to run together.

00:17:33.852 --> 00:18:16.614
And He said this word: 'Purity will be at a premium in the last days.'This will become the most important survival skill for the body of Christ.

00:18:16.615 --> 00:18:38.239
Not canned foods and dried foods or water or anything else; this will become the most important—exclamation point—the revelation of the power and the authority of the name of Jesus.

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:49.428
Exactly! When God is saying 'prepare,'He's not talking about buying your $177,777 'good luck'dried food package where your family can eat for five years in a cave.

00:18:49.429 --> 00:19:05.479
If He speaks to you, you're going to know it. He can tell you how long it lasts, when it's coming, where it's coming from, and you'll have time to go do it.

00:19:05.480 --> 00:19:11.261
I'm not against savings accounts or having food put back or water or buying at a discount or buying in bulk.

00:19:11.262 --> 00:19:17.703
I'm not against any of that; what I'm against is the fear that's causing you to do it and the trust in it.

00:19:17.704 --> 00:19:25.453
Because I can guarantee you: if you've got three weeks of water, then what, big boy?

00:19:25.454 --> 00:19:34.575
Is that all you're going to live, three weeks past the provisions? Come on, now.

00:19:34.576 --> 00:19:58.759
This will be the most important survival skill, bar none, in the end times: the revelation of the power and the authority of the mighty name that's above every name, where we can handle life, that will bring fish, water, and bread in the desert where there's no river.

00:19:58.760 --> 00:20:06.510
God can fly bread to Elijah on ravens; He is not going to have a problem getting your stuff to you.

00:20:06.511 --> 00:20:15.593
I don't care what kind of pandemic is going on; we're not going to run out of trees.

00:20:15.594 --> 00:20:24.552
So you're going to have heat? Go cut some trees and have a fire. It amazed me at Y2K, the people that just went crazy.

00:20:24.553 --> 00:20:32.605
I was ministering around Chicago, and people were just acting a fool. I said, 'Y'all are scared of running out of water?

00:20:32.606 --> 00:20:47.226
You've got Lake Michigan right there!'But people go nuts; fear will make you stupid.

00:20:47.227 --> 00:20:52.974
I'm telling you right now: the authority of that name—glory to God—the authority of that name!

00:20:52.975 --> 00:20:56.261
Yes, I said glory to God, the authority of that name, the authority of the name!

00:20:56.262 --> 00:20:58.989
We're going to launch into it; we're going for it, glory to God!

00:20:58.990 --> 00:21:09.775
Right here, you're about to see revelation of the name of Jesus explode all over the world because, if it doesn't, the Holy Ghost can't come finish this harvest.

00:21:09.776 --> 00:21:21.326
There's going to be a massive harvest. I won't be the only one preaching it, but He told me that, as a matter of fact, I would be one of the tips of the spear, so I'm getting after it, sir.

00:21:21.327 --> 00:21:31.959
I'm about to get after it because, by and large, my generation has little to no revelation of it, and what revelation they did learn thirty years ago, they lost.

00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:49.403
They're not operating in it, but there is glory in that name, there's power in that name, and I'm named with that name.

00:21:49.404 --> 00:21:56.119
Whatever that name can do, I can do. Anything that name can do, I can do.

00:21:56.120 --> 00:22:04.414
I've been given the name, and whatever the name can do, I can do because it's my name.

00:22:04.415 --> 00:22:12.620
I'll never be intimidated in front of a sick person as long as I'm putting my hands on them in that name.

00:22:12.621 --> 00:22:22.173
I'll never be intimidated in front of a demon-possessed person as long as I know when the devil manifests, I've got that name to use.

00:22:22.174 --> 00:22:41.890
There'll be no banker's statement, no doctor's report, no lawyer's plea or suit, no government transaction, no threatening letter from the IRS.

00:22:41.891 --> 00:23:08.183
There'll never be anything that we have to draw back from or be intimidated by as long as we know we've got that name.

00:23:08.184 --> 00:23:15.909
I tell you, I'm totally convinced of this. This is so strong. Can you understand?

00:23:15.910 --> 00:23:20.676
We just went through a portal; we literally just went through a shift. We just stepped somewhere today.

00:23:20.677 --> 00:23:28.239
This is the ninth month of the year; this thing's coming to pass for us. So, here we are. We have power and authority.

00:23:28.240 --> 00:23:46.558
He's warning about what He saw coming, and it's like He said: 'Stay on point.'We have to focus on what the Lord has told us, that we have power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:23:46.559 --> 00:23:57.871
We have to understand that we have the authority of the name of Jesus back in us, just like we are ambassadors of the Lord Jesus Christ on this earth.

00:23:57.872 --> 00:24:12.883
As we take our place—like I was trying to tell you all before—an ambassador of America has all of America backing him: the Treasury Department, the military, everything.

00:24:12.884 --> 00:24:27.050
Here we are as believers; we go in the name of Jesus and we're ambassadors of the Lord Jesus Christ, ambassadors of heaven in this earth.

00:24:27.051 --> 00:24:35.192
We are seated with Him in the heavenlies, and so we're coming down here and we're operating in that name.

00:24:35.193 --> 00:24:47.373
It's what's backing us. It's like the name of America is backing the ambassador for whoever is going in that name.

00:24:47.374 --> 00:24:52.634
So we're coming in the name of Jesus; we're coming in the name of heaven.

00:24:52.635 --> 00:25:03.599
We're going as ambassadors into the earth, and we have all heaven backing us. So what I'm trying to say to you is we have nothing to fear.

00:25:03.600 --> 00:25:10.820
We have nothing to worry about because Jesus Christ dwells on the inside of us and all heaven is backing us.

00:25:10.821 --> 00:25:16.699
We have all the angels, the military, we have all of the Treasury Department, cattle on a thousand hills.

00:25:16.700 --> 00:25:25.005
Everything of the Lord's is His, and the fullness thereof. It's all the Lord's; everything we need is in that name.

00:25:25.006 --> 00:25:41.044
If we go before Him, take communion daily, and seek His face, we have the medical team; we can lay hands on the sick and they'll recover, we can cast out devils, and we can raise the dead.

00:25:41.045 --> 00:25:49.873
We can do it all in that name. So I just want to encourage you all today that we know that these storms are coming.

00:25:49.874 --> 00:25:57.498
We know that it says in the last days that wars and rumors of wars, we'll see plagues and pestilence and things coming.

00:25:57.499 --> 00:26:03.839
We know that all that stuff's coming, but we have authority.

00:26:03.840 --> 00:26:10.481
As He is, so are we in this world, and we are able to do what He did.

00:26:10.482 --> 00:26:17.856
Greater works will you do than what He did. Greater works! What more could we do?

00:26:17.857 --> 00:26:23.307
Well, you know, we lay hands on the sick, we cast out devils freely. Freely we've been given, freely we give it out.

00:26:23.308 --> 00:26:28.085
And so I'm just trying to encourage you all today to get in your Bibles.

00:26:28.086 --> 00:26:37.009
I want you to put the prophetic ministry out of business because you have the ability to hear the Lord for yourself.

00:26:37.010 --> 00:26:46.548
You don't need prophetic people to tell you what's coming. You can hear God for yourself. You can get in the word, you can fast, you can pray.

00:26:46.549 --> 00:26:54.954
And yeah, He speaks to His prophetic voices—I believe that for these end times—but there's a lot of people that are desperate.

00:26:54.955 --> 00:27:00.165
They email me: 'What can I do to invest? Where should I be moving? Where should I be living?

00:27:00.166 --> 00:27:05.214
Where should I be going with my kids and my family?'We're desperate; we don't hear the Lord.

00:27:05.215 --> 00:27:12.101
Well, I'm going to tell you the Bible says that a sheep knows His voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:27:12.102 --> 00:27:20.451
I believe with all my heart the Spirit of the Lord dwells on the inside of you, and you don't need a man telling you what to do.

00:27:20.452 --> 00:27:25.894
We're not fortune tellers; we hear what the Lord is saying to us to tell you about what's coming.

00:27:25.895 --> 00:27:33.842
But I'm telling you the same Spirit of God that dwells on the inside of me and talks to me on a daily basis, He'll talk to you.

00:27:33.843 --> 00:27:44.849
And I'm telling you if you read His word and you pray and you seek His face every day and you spend time with Him, it's just like a relationship with your wife.

00:27:44.850 --> 00:27:50.207
If you only talk to her once a week, you're not going to have a good relationship.

00:27:50.208 --> 00:27:56.680
If you only talk to her twice a week, you're only going to have a semi-okay relationship.

00:27:56.681 --> 00:28:21.191
But the more you spend time with her, the more you have fellowship with her, and you sit on the couch at night and you have fellowship—you hold her and you tell her, 'Baby, I love you,'and you go out on dates and you go out to dinner—and you fellowship with that bride you're married to, it builds a relationship.

00:28:21.192 --> 00:28:37.228
Over the course of twenty-three years of marriage, the relationship that I have with my wife today is nothing compared to when we first got married.

00:28:37.229 --> 00:28:46.154
A year into it, you think, 'Oh, I really know this person,'but I didn't know her at all back then.

00:28:46.155 --> 00:28:51.379
Here we are twenty-three years in, and I find something new about her every day.

00:28:51.380 --> 00:28:58.296
How bad do you want a relationship? How hungry and how much of a desire do you have for a relationship with the Lord?

00:28:58.297 --> 00:29:07.918
I'm trying to compare it to a marriage, and it is like that. But I'm trying to tell you all: how hungry, how desperate, how bad do you want a relationship with Jesus?

00:29:07.919 --> 00:29:15.441
It's when you spend time with Him daily and sit at His feet. I seek Him and I say, 'Jesus, I need your fresh touch today.

00:29:15.442 --> 00:29:19.999
I'm dry. I need a fresh touch of the Holy Ghost today. I need a drink.

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:25.475
I'm so thirsty, Lord. I'm so desperate for more of you. You are the potter, I'm the clay.

00:29:25.476 --> 00:29:35.198
I need you today, Lord.'And even whenever you're having a hard day, you run to Him.

00:29:35.199 --> 00:29:40.694
You don't run from Him; you run to Him. When you sin, you don't run from Him; you run to Him.

00:29:40.695 --> 00:29:49.791
When we mess up and we sin, your sin is none of the devil's business. He tempted you; he causes us to stumble and fall.

00:29:49.792 --> 00:29:54.151
The Bible says that he's the great tempter and the accuser of the brethren.

00:29:54.152 --> 00:30:03.988
But I'm telling you when you run to the blood and you run to the name of Jesus and you say, 'Father, I need you. I'm desperate. I've messed up.'He's able.

00:30:03.989 --> 00:30:12.711
He said if you confess your sins, He is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you of all your unrighteousness.

00:30:12.712 --> 00:30:17.273
